{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_11.png?t=1731642115\" />CineSim offers an immersive 3D environment that allows you explore the world of media production. Want to practice lighting a scene, designing a set, or framing the perfect shot? With CineSim, you can do all that and more! Whether you're new to media production or looking to enhance your skills, CineSim provides an intuitive, hands-on platform where you can dive into the world of filmmaking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create your own cinematic scenes or explore pre-set templates. CineSim allows you to practice real-world production techniques, all within a stunningly realistic environment powered by Unreal Engine 5\u2014right from your desktop.\u00a0Unlock a complete cinematic experience with advanced tools, more assets, and full creative control! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_4.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_5.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_11_copy.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy-to-navigate design for users of all skill levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drag-and-drop functionality for quick scene creation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Custom Control Rig for characters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_11_copy_2.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High-quality 3D visuals powered by Unreal Engine 5.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Real-time previews to instantly view changes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_11_copy_3.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock all pre-set templates: 15 pre-set templates.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build custom scenes using the &quot;Blank&quot; template.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Access 2000+ assets, including characters, props, facial expressions, and environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize characters with various facial expressions and actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_11_copy_4.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full control over camera angles, lens types, and focal lengths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Preview and adjust camera settings in real-time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Advanced lighting control for angles and color temperatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full weather control for time of day, sun rotation, and fog density.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/Artboard_11_copy_5.png?t=1731642115\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Capture high-quality images of your scenes to showcase your work.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img cla